creator: wollman+apache@csail.mit.edu
text:
The SSLLog and SSLLogLevel directives have been removed from mod_ssl.  However,
the mod_ssl reference documentation does not describe how to get the
functionality they provided, and in fact does not even mention that they have
been removed.  (I had to grep through the source code to find them.)  The
"Compatibiliy" documentation, which is supposed to describe how to migrate from
other SSL implementations to mod_ssl, still claims that they exist.
